# NOTE: worker/src/targets.json is now COMMITTED as the single source of truth
# for the puzzle answer set. It is deliberately not a secret — the crops in
# public/pieces already reveal each shard's region, and the security model never
# relied on hiding the coordinate JSON (the answer is withheld from the client at
# RUNTIME by the Worker, which sends shards by index only). Committing it stops
# the file from silently drifting/being clobbered and changing prod answers.
cloudflared/
